    <description>Peak torque limit indexed by RPM. Raw 7500 = factory 400 Nm for OM612, scale 400/7500 = 0.05333 Nm per raw count. The 19 rows cover RPM bands from idle (~750 rpm) to redline (~4500 rpm). Caps the maximum torque the ECU will deliver regardless of fuel/boost requests.</description>
